### 7. Hackathon codebase vs rebuild

| Area         | Hackathon (legacy)                   | Rebuild                                                |
| ------------ | ------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------ |
| Language     | JavaScript                           | TypeScript                                             |
| Navigation   | Stack + Tab (React Navigation 5)     | Expo Router, file-based routes                         |
| Global state | Context (`User`, `Progress`)         | Zustand + Firebase for auth; Query for server state    |
| Data / API   | Direct HTTP-style calls from client  | TanStack Query, cache, persistence, online/focus hooks |
| UI           | styled-components, Gifted Chat, etc. | NativeWind, custom message UI                          |
| Firebase     | Web-compat style SDK                 | `@react-native-firebase/*` modules                     |

